@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000
@adminKey = change-me-admin-key
@tenantKey = demo-acme-api-key

### Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Provision a tenant (copy the returned api_key if one is not supplied)
POST {{baseUrl}}/tenants
X-API-Key: {{adminKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "New Distribution Co",
  "external_odoo_instance_id": "odoo-newco",
  "api_key": "newco-local-secret-key"
}

### List tenant customers
GET {{baseUrl}}/customers?page=1&page_size=20&sync_status=pending
X-API-Key: {{tenantKey}}

### Create a customer idempotently
POST {{baseUrl}}/customers
X-API-Key: {{tenantKey}}
Idempotency-Key: customer-demo-001
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Prismatic Demo Buyer",
  "email": "buyer@example.com",
  "phone": "+1-555-0199"
}

### Poll pending integration events (Prismatic flow trigger)
GET {{baseUrl}}/integration-events?status=pending&page_size=100
X-API-Key: {{tenantKey}}

### Odoo result callback (replace entity_id)
POST {{baseUrl}}/webhooks/odoo
X-API-Key: {{tenantKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "entity_type": "order",
  "entity_id": "replace-with-order-id",
  "external_id": "ODOO-SO-10042",
  "invoice_status": "invoiced",
  "payment_status": "paid",
  "delivery_status": "delivered",
  "synchronization_result": "success",
  "metadata": {"prismatic_execution_id": "example-execution-id"}
}
